<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>6.9领导层会议 - 数据可视化看板</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif; background: #0f172a; }
        .glass { background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.1); }
        .card-hover { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .card-hover:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .progress-bar { transition: width 1.5s ease-out; }
        .pulse-dot { animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.4; } }
        .tab-active { border-bottom: 2px solid #60a5fa; color: #60a5fa; }
        .scroll-hide::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
        .scroll-hide { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }
        .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    </style>
<base target="_blank">
</head>
<body class="text-slate-200 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="glass sticky top-0 z-50 px-6 py-4">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-white text-lg"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold gradient-text">6.9领导层会议数据看板</h1>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">商办与公寓运营数据汇报及管培生系统建设项目</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                <div class="text-right hidden md:block">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">会议时间</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold">2026/6/9</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right hidden md:block">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">会议时长</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold">2小时30分钟</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 pulse-dot"></div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400 font-medium">已完成</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 space-y-6">
        <!-- 参会人员 -->
        <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 fade-in">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-users text-blue-400"></i> 参会人员
                </h2>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">11人</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 text-sm font-medium">Jenny</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-300 text-sm font-medium">黄一萧</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-pink-500/10 border border-pink-500/20 text-pink-300 text-sm font-medium">Bella</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium">王倩</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-300 text-sm font-medium">蔡心宇</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-rose-500/10 border border-rose-500/20 text-rose-300 text-sm font-medium">Angela</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300 text-sm font-medium">黄欢欢</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm font-medium">汪顺</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 text-orange-300 text-sm font-medium">王韬</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/20 text-teal-300 text-sm font-medium">邵吴慧</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 text-violet-300 text-sm font-medium">安子玥</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 关键指标卡片 -->
        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 fade-in">
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 card-hover">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">公寓二次租金收入</span>
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-building text-blue-400 text-sm"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">867.1<span class="text-sm text-slate-400 ml-1">万元</span></p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">1-5月累计</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 card-hover">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">商办账期收入</span>
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-briefcase text-purple-400 text-sm"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">681<span class="text-sm text-slate-400 ml-1">万元</span></p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">完成预算 35.84%</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 card-hover">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">腾跃违约欠款</span>
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-red-400 text-sm"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-400">46.8<span class="text-sm text-slate-400 ml-1">万元</span></p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">已通过押金抵扣部分</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 card-hover">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">物业费收入</span>
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd text-emerald-400 text-sm"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">133.2<span class="text-sm text-slate-400 ml-1">万元</span></p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">对外收取</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 图表区域 -->
        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 fade-in">
            <!-- 公寓收支结构 -->
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 card-hover">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-pie-chart text-blue-400"></i> 公寓1-5月收支结构
                </h3>
                <div class="h-64">
                    <canvas id="apartmentChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 商办预算完成率 -->
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 card-hover">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-bar text-purple-400"></i> 商办预算完成情况
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1">
                            <span>当前完成率</span>
                            <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">35.84%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-3 bg-slate-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full progress-bar" style="width: 35.84%"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1">
                            <span>补足欠款后</span>
                            <span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">38.31%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-3 bg-slate-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-500 rounded-full progress-bar" style="width: 38.31%"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded-lg bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/10">
                        <p class="text-sm text-red-300"><i class="fas fa-info-circle mr-1"></i> 腾跃违约导致46.8万元应收款未收回</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 物业数据 -->
        <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 fade-in">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-tools text-emerald-400"></i> 物业部门收支明细
            </h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/10">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-2">收入项</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>对外物业费</span><span class="font-semibold text-emerald-300">133.2万</span></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>内部结算(公寓)</span><span class="font-semibold">10.9万</span></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>其他收入</span><span class="font-semibold">13.3万</span></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>停车费(一次性)</span><span class="font-semibold text-amber-300">85.8万</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/10">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-2">支出项</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>人力成本</span><span class="font-semibold text-red-300">178.2万</span></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>维修保养</span><span class="font-semibold">35.3万</span></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>福利费</span><span class="font-semibold">23.8万</span></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between"><span>办公行政</span><span class="font-semibold">12.9万</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/10 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-2">最终利润</p>
                    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400">20.7<span class="text-lg">万元</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 世赢欠款追踪 -->
        <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 fade-in">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar text-amber-400"></i> 世赢公司欠款及还款计划
            </h3>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full text-sm">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-700">
                            <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 font-medium">时间节点</th>
                            <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 font-medium">支付内容</th>
                            <th class="text-right py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 font-medium">金额</th>
                            <th class="text-center py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 font-medium">状态</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/30">
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">6月8日</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">5月租金及物业费</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-semibold">~11.3万</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center"><span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 text-xs">已支付</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/30">
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">6月15日</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">租金</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-semibold">10万</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center"><span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs">待支付</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/30">
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">6月18/22日</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">租金</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-semibold">16万</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center"><span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs">待支付</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/30">
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">6月25日</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">物业费及水电费</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-semibold">-</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center"><span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs">待支付</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/30">
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">7月15日</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">7月全额租金</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-semibold">26万</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center"><span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-500/10 text-slate-400 text-xs">计划中</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="hover:bg-slate-800/30">
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">7月31日前</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4">补缴7月部分租金</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-semibold">10-15万</td>
                            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center"><span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-500/10 text-slate-400 text-xs">计划中</span></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 管培生项目 -->
        <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 fade-in">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket text-violet-400"></i> 管培生系统建设项目
            </h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">项目周期</span>
                        <span class="text-sm font-semibold">2026.6.1 - 8.31</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">团队规模</span>
                        <span class="text-sm font-semibold">6名管培生 + 2名原有员工</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">当前阶段</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-xs">需求澄清 → 方案评估</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-2">核心模块</p>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 text-xs">人事</span>
                            <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-300 text-xs">法务用印</span>
                            <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300 text-xs">财务账务</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="h-48">
                    <canvas id="projectChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 待办事项 -->
        <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 fade-in">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-tasks text-rose-400"></i> 会议待办事项 (9项)
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/30 hover:border-rose-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-rose-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                        <span class="text-xs text-rose-400 font-bold">1</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium">安子玥负责制作本次会议纪要并进行后续会议邀约</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">行政支持</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/30 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                        <span class="text-xs text-blue-400 font-bold">2</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium">黄燕婷在三个月内梳理并系统化过去三年的人事流程，实现人事工作的自动化和服务界面化</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">人事模块 | 截止: 2026.8.31</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/30 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                        <span class="text-xs text-purple-400 font-bold">3</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium">法务团队在三个月内完成过去三年法务工作量的还原与系统化，明确审核职责和流程</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">法务模块 | 截止: 2026.8.31</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/30 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                        <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400 font-bold">4</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium">财务与账务团队每月15日前在项目管理系统中提交上月税务统计表、资产负债表及损益表</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">财务模块 | 循环任务</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/30 hover:border-amber-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                        <span class="text-xs text-amber-400 font-bold">5</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium">邵吴慧协助韩泽总将商办业务数据整合至HMS 2.0系统，并推动合同管理流程上线</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">系统建设</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/30 hover:border-cyan-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                        <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 font-bold">6</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium">黄欢欢在三个月内将原有管理系统经验固化到新系统中，并确保每日现金流数据可被黄总实时查询</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">系统建设 | 截止: 2026.8.31</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/30 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                        <span class="text-xs text-indigo-400 font-bold">7</span>
